trabBuild
=========

Update and build your python projects in one step.


Install
-------

For editable install from the trabBuild directory. ::

    pip install -e .

Or install from setup.py ::

    python setup.py install


Usage
-----

Navigate to the directory with your package and setup.py file and type. ::

    $ trabbuild

***NOTE***
**Package version must be specified in setup.py with this format** ::

    __version__ = "x.x.x"

You will be prompted to enter a new version number that's higher than the current version.


